\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b I looked away as I wasn\uc0{\u8217}t interested in good guys, I just wanted a good-looking girl who was seated behind me. After a few minutes I asked Shady who the girl was and if she had a boyfriend in the school, but he assured me that she was single and very friendly. Osoro then said Shady has eyes for the girl too. He and Samuel who is my cousin have bet, the first one to win will be collecting one chapati from the loser until the end of the term. \uc0{\u8220}Guess who is going to collect all the chapatis?\uc0{\u8221} I said. We all laughed, and then Samuel joined the conversation from the other first row. He sat near the door at the corner. \uc0{\u8220}Why are you guys laughing and what are you talking about?\uc0{\u8221} he inquired }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b Samuel was the class topper. He was supposed to finish the previous year but something was wrong with his registration, so he repeated the class that year. }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b The teacher entered the class, \uc0{\u8220}Good morning class? Get out your chemistry books\uc0{\u8221} he said.We replied to him in unison \uc0{\u8220}Good morning Mr. Chacha\uc0{\u8221}}}\par
