\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b She pulled out her book from the locker and read on with the most soothing and sweetest voice ever. The sound of her voice made my ears locked with my eardrums then made a music and rhythm that lasted from ear to ear as she read on. I pretended I was not looking but I found myself smiling, I couldn\uc0{\u8217}t help seeing her lips moving. The teacher interrupted my concentration, \uc0{\u8220}Seems like we have a new student, what is your name young man?\uc0{\u8221} he asked. }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}Jones Majun, sir\uc0{\u8221} I replied }}\par
