\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b My mind recollected itself and as soon as I gained my sense, I broke my shyness. }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}Hi, am Majun, and you?\uc0{\u8221} I said with a trembling voice. }}\par
