\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}John Terry, do you play football?\uc0{\u8221} I asked }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}No, I don\uc0{\u8217}t. And who is John Terry?\uc0{\u8221} }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}Chelsea football club captain who plays as a centreback,\uc0{\u8221} I said.}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b I was struggling, I could tell by how I was sweating in the morning, did I mention that it was a cold morning before.? It was like I had been possessed and I needed exorcism to get her spirit out. I have never come across such a lady before, maybe Katrina or Nyariak or Lydia Mark that comes closer to her but still.}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b  But there was one lady I could compare to her; Sarah Abraham was also a beast of beauty. Then there was something about this Terry girl that I couldn\uc0{\u8217}t wrap my head around. How can a human be so perfect and be unpredictable with the moves?}}\par
