\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b My head was relaxed and my heart got lighter with every word we spoke. We exchanged funny stories and shared a lot of laughter. I have never laughed like that around a lady for quite some time until that day. There was some innocence in her words as they passed through my heart to my head before they were amplified and translated into images.}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b There was something about her behaviours that I hadn\uc0{\u8217}t seen in the class, she was as lively as a cricket and carefree like a bird freed from the cage as if she had no problems. We carried on with the conversation with no boundaries; she told me about few things about the class and the teachers. I could see the excitement in her eyes. I made her laugh uncontrollably with the manner of jokes, I have always been a clown around ladies I like and very strategic with words. She couldn\uc0{\u8217}t help but cover her mouth with two hands to avoid being loud. I wish we could continue longer but \uc0{\u160}a good dancer is he who knows when to leave the dance floor.}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b I have never felt that way before. The feeling was something that I had never believed I would fall for one day. }}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b I have fallen in love before but not to the point I lose myself in someone else and be so free and weightless just in a second. Wait, was I not in love before? What was it that I have had with these other girls? I guess I will never know, but for once I felt my life was complete with her. }}\par
