\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b Our Maths teacher entered and to my surprise, he is the school director but no one can tell since he was a young guy in his early 30s. \uc0{\u8220}Shady, unafanya nini hapo surely?\uc0{\u8221} this is to say what are you doing there Shady in Swahili as he looks through the page. Shady came back and he sat down smiling. \uc0{\u8220}Sikujua pia wewe unakuwanga na vituko?\uc0{\u8221} I didn\uc0{\u8217}t know you were full of jokes too, he said while smiling. \uc0{\u8220}So, today we are going to learn what Matrix transformation is\uc0{\u8221} he turned and wrote on the board as he talked \uc0{\u8220}Majun, I hope you have covered this topic in your previous school?\uc0{\u8221} I looked around and all eyes were on me. \uc0{\u8220}Yes mwalimu, we were almost through with Statistics Two before we closed the school for the December holiday,\uc0{\u8221} I said. }}\par
