\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0\b \uc0{\u8220}Okay, Sam how is it supposed to be done?\uc0{\u8221} asked the teacher handing out a white chalk to Majok. Sam got up and walked towards the board and he did the sum in less than a minute and sat down. Terry also followed and she sat down. I looked at her in a glance to say \uc0{\u8220}Don\uc0{\u8217}t worry, if you allow me to be your lover you won\uc0{\u8217}t struggle with simple sums like that matrix again in your school life\uc0{\u8221} I was about to unleash my soap opera moves on her, after all, I have watched so many that I have qualified to be a romantic guy. Charming words and gentle touches, a style so rare. I learned it from William Levy. }}\par
